 THE MODERATOR: Questions, please. 

 Q. I understand you're a father. I was just wondering what was it was like to play tennis and be a father and how you manage both. 
 STANISLAS WAWRINKA: It's okay normally. Since I'm father I'm playing pretty well. I try to travel a little bit with my family, but actually they are not here this time.
 But that's fine. I'm pretty happy with my game. Since I'm father, I think I'm playing pretty well. 







